{"tid":619163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歐盟、日本加入貿易戰","createTime":"2018-04-06T11:41:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-08T18:22:27.000Z","uid":27688,"like":49,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"2b8696522da68e39ad843479e80c26d9b09bcd8e","tid":619163,"uid":27688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:41:28.000Z","msg":"【歐盟、日本加入貿易戰】<br />\n【聯合美國商討中國知識產權問題】<br />\n<br />\n內地第一財經取得兩份世貿組織(WTO)文件，顯示歐盟和日本要求加入美國在WTO就中國歧視性的技術許可(跟國際知識產權協定相違背)，跟中國政府磋商。<br />\n<br />\n歐盟在WTO申請文件中指出，歐盟對外出口高科技產品和高科技知識密集型的服務產品，為此對歐盟產品的智慧財產權的保護具有重要性。歐盟方面估計每年對外出口的高科技產品在6800億歐元左右，其中歐盟每年向中國出口300億歐元的高科技產品。<br />\n<br />\n#歐日美聯盟<br />\n#知識產權<br />\n#貿易戰<br />\n#有線中國組"},{"pid":"4a85a069900de257c5b2206dafd0d31be691f5c3","tid":619163,"uid":118502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:48:00.000Z","msg":"中國仲有nigga,我国必胜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85aa70b85b25e68864d5c9dc89535dd8c3d9e333","tid":619163,"uid":70786,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:48:33.000Z","msg":"八國聯軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2751997b805d4d3993dbdb77fbc2abe5c9799c77","tid":619163,"uid":91721,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T11:56:11.000Z","msg":"所以話如果中國要用WTO程序解決問題，就要先做返好自己初時嘅應承嘅嘢"},{"pid":"fb61f99b7a2f8641ec60831898af366cae377d10","tid":619163,"uid":26752,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-06T12:45:33.000Z","msg":"新八國聯軍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美軍來到我帶路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337d3cc0f8dfa7e6f32d84a248670cfcc7938a6d","tid":619163,"uid":34530,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyT